author: National Geographic
description:
Take a journey further along the Silk Road and visit one of its less-visited stops—Khiva, Uzbekistan. Posed on the edge of the vast desert, explore Itchan Kala fortress with its centuries-old monuments or head to the new Silk Road-themed Arda Khiva resort with its water park and amphitheater.

description:
